.002">Multidetector Computed Tomography of Nonosseous Thoracic Trauma</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Kristopher W. Cummings</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Cylen Javidan-Nejad</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Sanjeev Bhalla</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">2014Apr1 | Seminars in Roentgenology, Vol. 49, No. 2</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1053/j.ro.2014.01.002">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.1016/j.ijcard.2013.12.049"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.ijcard.2013.12.049">Delayed cardiac tamponade following management of a massive hemothorax related to a penetrating thoracic trauma</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Maximilien Sochala</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Linda Aïssou</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Emmanuel Sorbets</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Natalia Pop</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Carla Sleiman</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">François-Xavier Goudot</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Christophe Meune</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">2014Mar1 | International Journal of Cardiology, Vol. 172, No. 1</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.ijcard.2013.12.049">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.1186/1749-8090-8-158"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://doi.org/10.1186/1749-